<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>للزِّرَاعَة<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>وَلم يدْرك<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p58"></span>الزَّرْع<a href="#p58" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>فِيهَا لتَقْصِيره<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>أَي الْمُسْتَعِير<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>بِتَأْخِير الزِّرَاعَة قلع<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>الْمُعير<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p63"></span>مجَّانا<a href="#p63" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>وَيلْزمهُ أَيْضا تَسْوِيَة الأَرْض أما إِذا لم يحصل مِنْهُ تَقْصِير فانه<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>